{
 "name": "RPlog_Medical_Consultation",
 "title": "Medical Consultation in Fountain Square",
 "summary": "In Fountain Square in Plaxton on Caspar, the bacta-allergic doctor Lynae Cassius, recovering from a stormtrooper beating, is fishing a ball out of a fountain when the Corellian operative Malif finds her with the battle surgeon Xar'on Tanner in tow. Tanner examines the explosive monitoring device manacled to her wrist and grimly determines that it is wired directly to her heart, set to detonate if her pulse rises. As a silent cloaked figure shadows the group, Malif relocates everyone to Lynae's cabin in Orlaeno, where the bald stranger reveals himself and asks who would do such a thing. Tanner paces and grumbles over the lethal device while Lynae absorbs the danger she is in, the consultation underscoring how thoroughly she has been trapped.",
